guidoengine
Class guidoscoremap

java.lang.Object
  guidoengine.guidoscoremap

public final class guidoscoremap
extends java.lang.Object

A Guido score map.
A guido score map describes the relations between the time and graphic space. It is typically used as argument of the guidscore adjusted mappings methods.
